{"word":"G3916 - παραχρῆμα - parachrēma - par-akh-ray'-mah - Forthwith","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραχρῆμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parachrēma</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-akh-ray'-mah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Forthwith</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உடனே, சீக்கிரமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"immediately, forthwith, instantly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G5536 - χρῆμα - chrēma - khray'-mah/5536\">G5536</a> (in its original sense); <i>at the thing</i> itself, that is, <i>instantly:</i> - forthwith, immediately, presently, straightway, soon.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}